1.3 (2007-05-06)
* Better looking disable menu entry
* Menu entry for starting the stream
* Checkbox for disabling new version check

1.2 (2007-02-24)
* Auto-check for new version
* Setting to avoid display of seconds 
* About dialog to display version number
* Possibility to disable the application
* Save password and username between sessions in KWallet
* Avoid using 0 minutes intervals (which made SnakeTray go nuts)

